================================================================================
PINN with Gradient Surgery and Symmetry Enforcement (PyTorch)
================================================================================

Problem: Anisotropic diffusion on oval (elliptical) domain
A = diag(2.0, 0.5)
Ellipse semiaxes: a=2.0, b=1.0
Exact solution: v(x,y) = sqrt((x/a)^2 + (y/b)^2)
Backend: PyTorch 1.10.0 on cpu

================================================================================
EXPERIMENT: Impact of Gradient Surgery (Fair Comparison)
================================================================================
Seed: 42
Max epochs: 500, LR: 0.001
Early stopping: min_epochs=50, window=20, min_rel_improve=0.05, patience=2

